      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS MAXIMUS (1) was quickly into stride on debut to score by 1.3 lengths (22.31) at this track over 390m. Drawn to take advantage of good early pace. Should be in this for a long way. BART INTENTION (2) ran below best last time finishing seventh (20.61) over 350m at Healesville in a Grade 7. Can figure in the finish. PAW REYA (5) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd on March 17 over 410m at Horsham behind Paw Olympus beaten 2.25 lengths (23.48) in a Mix 6/7. Won at his only start from this box. Expected to be in the finish again. KODA (7) is on a run of three minor placings and will be in the mix again.",
